    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Post-1945 art movement building upon some of the aesthetic principles of Constructivism. Began in Russia, organized by Lev Nusberg (born 1937), Francisco Infante (born 1943) and Vyacheslav Koleychuk (born 1941).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
